                          {
                            "description": "This questionnaire has been designed for online mode. You may notice changes compared with the paper version, such as to the ordering of questions and sections."
                          },
                          {
                            "description": "There is additional guidance throughout the questionnaire. However, if you require support then please contact us on <a href=\"tel:03001234931\"target=\"_blank\"rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">0300 1234 931</a>or via email at <a href=\"mailto:surveys@ons.gov.uk?subject=Change%20of%20details%2012346789012A\"target=\"_blank\"rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">surveys@ons.gov.uk</a>"
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "id": "description",
                  "contents": [
                    {
                      "list": [
                        "This survey is conducted by the Office for National Statistics on behalf of the Department for Business and Trade (DBT).",
                        "DBT uses the information for monitoring trends in the construction industries.",
                        "You cannot appeal your selection. Your business was selected to give us a comprehensive view of the UK economy.",
                        {
                          "text": "Data should relate to {trad_as}.",
                          "placeholders": [
                            {
                              "placeholder": "trad_as",
                              "transforms": [
                                {
                                  "transform": "first_non_empty_item",
                                  "arguments": {
                                    "items": [
                                      {
                                        "source": "metadata",
                                        "identifier": "trad_as"
                                      },
                                      {
                                        "source": "metadata",
                                        "identifier": "ru_name"
                                      }
                                    ]
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        "You can provide informed estimates if actual figures are not available.",
                        "We will treat your data securely and confidentially.",
                        "You still need to complete this survey even if it does not seem relevant. All returns are important as it helps us produce better statistics.",
                        "You can save a copy of your answers at the end of this questionnaire using the &#x2018;Download as PDF&#x2019; button."
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "preview_content": {
                "id": "preview",
                "title": "Information you need",
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "description": "This survey collects information on marine dredged sand and gravel your business has sold in the reporting period."
                  },
                  {
                    "description": "The materials included in this survey are:"
                  },
                  {
                    "list": [
                      "sand",
                      "gravel, pebbles, shingle and flint",
                      "sand and gravel used for constructional fill"
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "description": "The survey has the following sections:"
                  }
                ],
                "questions": [
                  {
                    "question": "Material",
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "description": {
                          "text": "This section asks for confirmation of the materials sold for the period {ref_p_start_date} to {ref_p_end_date}.",
                          "placeholders": [
                            {
                              "placeholder": "ref_p_start_date",
                              "transforms": [
                                {
                                  "transform": "format_date",
                                  "arguments": {
                                    "date_to_format": {
                                      "source": "metadata",
                                      "identifier": "ref_p_start_date"
                                    },
                                    "date_format": "d MMMM yyyy"
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "placeholder": "ref_p_end_date",
                              "transforms": [
                                {
                                  "transform": "format_date",
                                  "arguments": {
                                    "date_to_format": {
                                      "source": "metadata",
                                      "identifier": "ref_p_end_date"
                                    },
                                    "date_format": "d MMMM yyyy"
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "question": "Details of sales",
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "description": "This section asks for the details of sales for the materials you have selected."
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "Report your figures in tonnes."
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "Sand:"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "sand produced for asphalt",
                          "sand produced for use in mortar",
                          "sand produced for concreting"
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "Gravel, pebbles, shingle and flint:"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "gravel coated with bituminous binder",
                          "gravel produced for concrete aggregate",
                          "other screened and graded gravels"
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "Sand and gravel used for constructional fill"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              "secondary_content": [
                {
                  "id": "secondary-content",
                  "contents": [
                    {
                      "title": "How we use your data"
                    },
                    {
                      "description": "For the benefit of industry, and the public generally, building materials information is published by DBT in <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/building-materials-and-components-monthly-statistics-2012\"target=\"_blank\"rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Monthly Statistics of Building Materials &amp; Components (this link opens in a new tab)</a>."
                    }
                  ]
                }
